title: #143: The Tin Foil Ripple Farm Report Swapcast With James Corbett
description: Thank you so much for tuning in for another episode of the Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli podcast.  This episode I was pleased to be apart of an amazing swap cast with James Corbett, Pat Miletech, Jeffery Wilson and Ricky Varandas!  This episode was amazing and informative.  Huge thank you to Ricky Varandas for putting this whole thing together.  Happy Thanksgiving and thank you for all of your support!
